{"type":"message","id":"0b4036fb","parentId":"f4d686bd","timestamp":"2026-03-03T00:02:17.235Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户让我去小红书看看最新的评论。这需要用 browser 工具来操作小红书。\n\n首先我得启动 browser，然后导航到小红书，找到我的账号和评论。\n\n不过我得先想想流程：\n1. 先 browser status 看看 browser 是不是已经开着\n2. 如果没开，browser start\n3. 导航到小红书 (xiaohongshu.com)\n4. 找到我的账号/消息通知，看评论\n\n让我先检查一下 browser 的状态。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d7cef5df34214667bffb10d3","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"status"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":34990,"output":232,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":35222,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772496129017}}
